<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>319</hymn_number>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Mirum pa innka hram pawngah a thu i, La-za-ruh cu a thi dengmang i,
 Vawlei sifah re-theihnak kha a in cang, A thih hnuah lunglawmhnak a hmuh.

[C1]
   Lawmhnak chungah khan vancungmi nih an lak, Vancung khua ah hlasak
   thawng a khat, Vancung sunparnak ah Khamhbawi nih a lak, A dawtmi hna
   sinah a kai cang.

[V2]
 Vawlei sifah in hnu ah kan thih ahcun, Kannih vialte kan lung aa lawm
 lai, Vawlei cung nunnak kha thilrit phorh bantuk, Ngaih-chiatnak mitthli
 tlaknak a si.

[C2]
   Lawmhnak chungah khan vancungmi nih an lak, Vancung khua ah hlasak
   thawng a khat, Vancung sunparnak ah Khamhbawi nih a lak, A dawtmi hna
   sinah a kai cang.

[V3]
 Jesuh hnu zulmi nih liam hmanh hna sehlaw, A sungmi hlawn vancung khua
 a um, Tukforh awlok-chonnak kha kan kal tak lai, Thlennak caan ah kan
 lung a lawm lai.

[C3]
   Lawmhnak chungah khan vancungmi nih an lak, Vancung khua ah hlasak
   thawng a khat, Vancung sunparnak ah Khamhbawi nih a lak, A dawtmi hna
   sinah a kai cang.

[V4]
 Pathian umnak leiah hmaiah fong chin tuah, Na fimnak kha Jesuh ca
 hmang tuah, Na tuannak tlawm hmanhseh, laksawng a tam lai, Vailam put in
 luchin naa chinh lai.

[C4]
   Lawmhnak chungah khan vancungmi nih an lak, Vancung khua ah hlasak
   thawng a khat, Vancung sunparnak ah Khamhbawi nih a lak, A dawtmi hna
   sinah a kai cang.</lyrics>
<title>VANCUNGMI NIH AN LAK CH319</title>
</song>